==English==
===Noun===
'''intention'''
#An act or instance of determining mentally upon some action or desired result  
#A [[course]] of [[action]] that a person [[intend]]s to [[follow]]
#* My '''intention''' was to marry a wealthy widow
'''intentions'''
#[[Purpose]] with [[respect]] to [[marriage]] for example
#* Does he have honourable '''intentions'''?

===Related terms===
*The [[road to hell is paved with good intentions]]

